Package tachyon.master.journal

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    JournalCheckpointStreamable
    This interface enables streaming out to the journal checkpoint.
    JournalEntry  
    JournalEntryRepresentable
    This interface enables representing a class as a JournalEntry.
    JournalFormatter
    This describes the interface for serializing and deserializing entries in the journal.
    JournalInputStream
    This input stream retrieves JournalEntry from journal checkpoint files and journal log files.
    JournalOutputStream
    This output stream writes JournalEntry objects to the journal.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Journal
    This encapsulates the journal for a master.
    JournalFormatter.Factory  
    JournalReader
    This class manages reading from the journal.
    JournalTailer
    This class tails the journal for a master.
    JournalTailerThread
    This thread continually tails the journal and applies it to the master, until the master initiates the shutdown of the thread.
    JournalWriter
    This class manages all the writes to the journal.
    JsonJournalFormatter  
    ReadOnlyJournal
    The read-only journal.
    ReadWriteJournal
    The read-write journal.
    SerializableJournalEntry
    A JournalEntry with a sequence number.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    JournalEntryType
    The types of entries that can be represented in the journal.
